## 🔧 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | Vanilla HTML, CSS, JavaScript (ES2022) |
| Auth & Database | [Supabase](https://supabase.com) (Auth + PostgreSQL) |
| Markdown Rendering | [marked.js](https://marked.js.org) |
| Backend API | FastAPI on [Railway](https://railway.app) |
| Job Queue | Redis (managed via Railway) |
| LLM Providers | Groq (LLaMA) + Google Gemini (fallback) |
| Fonts | Playfair Display + DM Sans (Google Fonts) |
| Deployment | Vercel (frontend) |

